Version: 0.9.1-rc.1

Copyright © 2026 @w{Charles Y. Choi}

@image{images/now-playing-screenshot,,,,png}

@strong{Now Playing} is an Emacs “now playing” interface for the macOS @uref{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Music_%28app%29, Music app}. @strong{Now Playing} provides a  Transient menu interface (@ref{Top,,,transient,}) to control the @strong{Music app} with the following commands:

@itemize
@item
Pause/Play (@code{SPC}@comma{} ▶/⏸)
@item
Previous (@code{p}@comma{} ⏮) and Next (@code{n}@comma{} ⏭) Track
@item
Open (launch) Music app (@code{o}@comma{} ♫)
@item
Increase (@code{<up>}) and Decrease (@code{<down>}) volume
@item
Refresh current track (@code{r}@comma{} ⟲)
@end itemize

@strong{Now Playing} is intended to be an ancillary interface to the Music app@comma{} providing only a subset of controls to it. It has no long-term agenda to be a full-featured client of @strong{Music app}.

If you enjoy using @strong{Now Playing}@comma{} please buy me a coffee to help support its development and maintenance.

@image{images/default-yellow,,,,png}

