@node Polling the Current Track
@section Polling the Current Track

@cindex Polling the Current Track

@strong{Now Playing} provides the capability to periodically log the current track into the special buffer @code{✱now playing log✱}.  The commands that control polling are listed below:

@table @asis
@item now-playing-start-polling-current-track
Poll current track with period @code{now-playing-poll-interval}.
@vindex now-playing-start-polling-current-track

@item now-playing-cancel-polling
Cancel poll timer.
@vindex now-playing-cancel-polling

@item now-playing-find-log
Find @code{✱now playing log✱} buffer.
@vindex now-playing-find-log

@item now-playing-is-polling-p
Predicate if logging the current track.
@vindex now-playing-is-polling-p
@end table


@subsubheading Polling Variable

Use the following variable to control sound volume changes.

@table @asis
@item now-playing-poll-interval
Poll interval (or period) in seconds
@vindex now-playing-poll-interval
@end table

